T02TD2207E:178b-1: pra ti shtha aa lam k'a ra /
T02TD2207E:178b-4: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2207E:178b-5: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi dang //
T02TD2207E:178b-6: zla ba lta bu'i mthu mnga' pa'i //
T02TD2207E:178b-7: sel cing snang bar byed pa yi //
T02TD2207E:178b-8: mnga' bdag rdo rje can la 'dud //
T02TD2207E:178b-9: chogs sogs nus pa tshogs byung bas //
T02TD2207E:178b-10: rab tu gnas pa bshad par bya //
T02TD2207E:178b-11: sngags pa yon tan kun ldan bas //
T02TD2207E:178b-12: bkra shis pa yi gnas dag tu //
T02TD2207E:178b-13: bsnyen pa rnam gsum rdzogs pa yis //
T02TD2207E:178b-14: lhag par gnas pa'i cho ga bya //
T02TD2207E:178b-15: mnga' dbul ba dang mchod pa brtsam //
T02TD2207E:178b-16: sngags kyis gnas pa'i don du ni //
T02TD2207E:178b-17: rgyas par rab gnas chen por blta //
T02TD2207E:178b-18: 'di ru cung zhig bsdus nas bstan //
T02TD2207E:178b-19: dang po rdul tshon dkyil 'khor bri //
T02TD2207E:178b-21: gru bzhi 'thas par byas pa la //
T02TD2207E:178b-22: thig ni legs par yongs btab la //
T02TD2207E:178b-23: sa tshon byin gyis brlab bya la //
T02TD2207E:178b-24: tshon rnams dgye ba'i rim pa ni //
T02TD2207E:178b-25: dbus kyi pho brang mthing ga la //
T02TD2207E:178b-27: shar gyi cha ni dkar po la //
T02TD2207E:178b-28: lho yi cha ni ser po ste //
T02TD2207E:178b-29: nub kyi cha ni dmar por snang //
T02TD2207E:178b-30: byang ni don yod grub pa ljang //
T02TD2207E:178b-31: mthing ga dkar dang ser dang dmar //
T02TD2207E:178b-32: ljang gu rnams su gsungs ba ni //
T02TD2207E:178b-34: sgo gnyis mtshams dang tva ra na //
T02TD2207E:178b-35: dra ba dra ba phyed pa dang //
T02TD2207E:178b-36: rgyan rnams kyis ni rnam par spras //
T02TD2207E:178b-37: tha ma srung ba phreng bas brgyan //
T02TD2207E:178b-38: dkyil 'khor gyi ni shar ngos su //
T02TD2207E:178b-39: dbang stegs steng du mdzes pa'i gdan //
T02TD2207E:178b-40: sku gsung thugs kyi rtags mchog bzhag / chu gsum 'dus pas khrus rnams bya //
T02TD2207E:178b-41: mchod pa'i yo byad rdzogs pa la //
T02TD2207E:179a-2: me tog rnams kyis yongs su klu bas //
T02TD2207E:179a-3: de nas rang gi bsam pa rdzog so //
T02TD2207E:179a-4: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gsal bar shes //
T02TD2207E:179a-5: dbang bskur ba la rab tu gnas //
T02TD2207E:179a-6: gsung ni h'i: las byung ba'i rigs //
T02TD2207E:179a-7: thugs ni mi bskyod rdo rje sems //
T02TD2207E:179a-8: sku ni rtag pa'i rang bzhin no ;
T02TD2207E:179a-9: / tsha tsha mtsho rten la sogs pa //
T02TD2207E:179a-10: sangs de zhu nas lce las ni //
T02TD2207E:179a-11: yi zhes tsha tsha mchod rten gyi //
T02TD2207E:179a-12: 'byung ba'i rgyu ru rnam par snang //
T02TD2207E:179a-13: lha khang 'bru yi rten las su //
T02TD2207E:179a-14: gong gi stobs kyis gang 'gyur ba //
T02TD2207E:179a-15: rang gi snad ba 'byung ba yin //
T02TD2207E:179a-16: slob dpon rab tu 'gying bcas pas ;
T02TD2207E:179a-17: / rdo rje dril bu ldan pa yis //
T02TD2207E:179a-18: bde gshegs nam mkhar sbyang drangs la //
T02TD2207E:179a-19: phyag 'tshal mchod bstod rgyas par bya //
T02TD2207E:179a-20: de nas phyag rgya bzhi ldan pas //
T02TD2207E:179a-21: rtags gsum dag lag gzhag par bya //
T02TD2207E:179a-22: des ni mchod pa rgyas pa'o //
T02TD2207E:179a-23: dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i lha la dbul //
T02TD2207E:179a-24: rin chen sna bdun lha mo brgyad //
T02TD2207E:179a-25: ma lus bstod cing bzod par gsol //
T02TD2207E:179a-26: gsang sngags rgyal po'i mtha' la ni //
T02TD2207E:179a-27: 'bru gsum yi ge btags pas ni //
T02TD2207E:179a-28: brgya rtsa brgyad nas stod rtsa brgyad //
T02TD2207E:179a-29: bzlas pa 'od zer gzhung bzhin bstim //
T02TD2207E:179a-30: zhu bas sku gsung thugs kyi rtags //
T02TD2207E:179a-31: rang rang rnams la gsal zhing rgyas //
T02TD2207E:179a-32: de la mchod pa sna tshogs kyang //
T02TD2207E:179a-33: dkon mchog skyabs chen rnams dang yang //
T02TD2207E:179a-34: ma lus lus pa med pa la //
T02TD2207E:179a-35: yang dag pa ru rab tu bsngags //
T02TD2207E:179a-36: gtor ma gnyis kyis gtsang rigs dang //
T02TD2207E:179a-37: bgegs dang rigs drug ma lus pa //
T02TD2207E:179a-38: gtor ma chen po sbyin du mchod ;
T02TD2207E:179a-39: / bskor ba bya zhing smon lam gdab //
T02TD2207E:179a-40: rab gnas bsdus pa'i cho ga ni //
T02TD2207E:179a-41: n'i l'am badzra mtha' bsgyur la //
T02TD2207E:179a-53: bi ma la su pa ri dharm'a karti ka na /
T02TD2207E:179a-60: stong dang brgya yi bzlas pa yis //
T02TD2207E:179a-61: sku gsungs thugs kyi ngo bo ru //
T02TD2207E:179a-62: byin gyis brlabs pa tsam ni bya //
T02TD2207E:179a-65: de ltar slob dpon de la ni //
T02TD2207E:179b-0: ci yod rang @179b gi nor rnams dbul //
T02TD2207E:179b-1: de nas rab gnas brtan pa yis //
T02TD2207E:179b-2: mgron rnams dgye zhing smon lam gdab //
T02TD2207E:179b-3: shi ba phyi yi cho ga yang //
T02TD2207E:179b-4: khrus byas rdul tshon gong bzhin bri //
T02TD2207E:179b-5: spyan drangs mdun gyi nam mkha' la //
T02TD2207E:179b-6: mchod cing ye shes me nas bsad //
T02TD2207E:179b-7: sbyang zing ro ni sreg rdzas su //
T02TD2207E:179b-8: me lha nyid la dbul bar bya //
T02TD2207E:179b-9: gtor ma cha gnyis cho ga yis //
T02TD2207E:179b-10: bsngo zhing smon lam gdab par bya //
T02TD2207E:179b-11: thig bsdus sa tshon tshul dbo //
T02TD2207E:179b-12: 'di brtsams pa yang dge ba yis //
T02TD2207E:179b-13: bdag dang khams gsum sems can rnams //
T02TD2207E:179b-14: nad dang sdug bsngal rtsad nas chod //
T02TD2207E:179b-15: zhing khams gtsang mar skye bar shog / dge slod n'a g'a rdzu nas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
